      <hedline>
        <hl1>TODAY IN BUSINESS | ANOTHER OPTIONS INQUIRY</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Pediatrix Medical Group says it is being investigated over stock options grants; will cooperate with investigation (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The Pediatrix Medical Group said it was being investigated by the United States attorney's office in Miami over grants of stock options. Pediatrix, a large provider of care for premature babies, said it would cooperate with the investigation and was working to complete its own review ''as soon as possible.'' The company reported last month that a preliminary examination found evidence that options were backdated.</p>
      </block>
